*portage-2.1.3.6 (15 Aug 2007)

  15 Aug 2007; Zac Medico <zmedico@gentoo.org> +portage-2.1.3.6.ebuild:
  2.1.3.6 bump. This fixes bugs #188449, #188619, #188782, and #188807.
  Most notable is the fix for bug #188782 which optimizes merge order
  for revdep-rebuild. Bug #181949 tracks all bugs fixed since 2.1.2.x.

*portage-2.1.3.5 (12 Aug 2007)

  12 Aug 2007; Zac Medico <zmedico@gentoo.org> +portage-2.1.3.5.ebuild:
  2.1.3.5 bump. This fixes bug #188559 (files are sometimes unmerged
  from lib dirs when they're supposed to stay installed). Bug #181949
  tracks all bugs fixed since 2.1.2.x.

